Howard & Angus - Acoustics and Psychoacoustics

One study has shown that tones most likely to be chosen are those whose higher partials coincide, and this is so not only in the case of tones of the harmonic spectrum but also tones of the inharmonic spectrum (Geary 1980, p.1785)


